ENTRY       EC 3.1.1.72                 Enzyme
NAME        acetylxylan esterase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Acting on ester bonds;
            Carboxylic-ester hydrolases
SYSNAME     acetylxylan esterase
REACTION    Deacetylation of xylans and xylo-oligosaccharides
COMMENT     Catalyses the hydrolysis of acetyl groups from polymeric xylan, acetylated xylose, acetylated glucose, alpha-napthyl acetate, p-nitrophenyl acetate but not from triacetylglycerol. Does not act on acetylated mannan or pectin.
HISTORY     EC 3.1.1.72 created 1999
